{
  "stem": "10181.5",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of the rest of Holland hadn't, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And most of the-- the major part of Holland, as a matter of fact, had only been liberated when the war was over.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was isolated from the rest of-- from the rest of Europe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like a-- like a fortress.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You ?] called it Fortress Holland, and-- and the Germans held it until the very end.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But Maastricht was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, they were liberated then, and at that-- everything-- the Americans had everything there, and a lot of hospitals.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was very sick by the time we got there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the rest of the people-- most-- many of the people were taken off the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But those who could were taken to nearby-- like a dispersement camp, where, you know, where they checked out who you were, where you wanted to go to.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you couldn't go everywhere yet because this was in May-- May '45.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- the major-- like Amsterdam-- these places had only been liberated, really, May 8, you know, when the war was over.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So-- and-- and they also had suffered-- also had suffered from starvation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So you-- they couldn't send people there in any case.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had to wait.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we were taken off the train, my sister and myself, because we were very sick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I think I had-- had developed typhus by that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was taken to one hospital, and my sister was taken to a different hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was taken to a hospital which-- Maastricht was very Catholic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And at the time, all the nurses were nuns.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And not only that, I was taken to a hospital which was inside a convent.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was a temporary hospital which had been established.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
